Package: smallcount
Type: Package
Title: Methods for Small Counts Stored in a Sparse Matrix 
Version: 0.99.0
Description: Functions for performing common tasks in genomics data analysis of
    small counts that are mostly zeros such as data generated by current single
    cell technologies.
